<!-- engage intro -->
<section class="engage_intro">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 style="color:#000000;font-weight: 600;font-size: 50px;">The Movement Team are here to support you and see the work in your city flourish</h2>
    <div class="engage_intro_grid "> <!-- container for 3 boxes -->
      <div class="engage_intro_grid_white"> <!-- box -->
        <h3>Engage</h3>
        <h2>Come to a Movement Day Gathering in your city</h2>
        <p>Major events that are held every 1-3 years and act as an accelerator for the long term vision of releasing beauty and shalom in Australian cities and towns. <br> Each Movement Day Gathering is between 1-3 days where the majority of Church Pastors and Christian Leaders gather to celebrate, connect, collaborate, catalyse, commission and tell Movement Stories that inspire action in other leaders to envisage and release beauty and shalom in their cities and towns.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="engage_intro_grid_grey"> <!-- box -->
        <h3>Engage</h3>
        <h2 style="color:#ffffff!important;">Come to a Movement Day Round Table in your city</h2>
        <p>These are smaller more targeted workshops, meetings, meals or prayer times that network Christian Pastors and leaders across city spheres to release city wide beauty and shalom.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="engage_intro_grid_white"> <!-- box -->
        <h3>Engage</h3>
        <h2>Create or Join a Movement Day Action Team in your city</h2>
        <p>These are focused meetings that bring together a team of local people to work on specific issues facing their city or town.</p>
      </div>            
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


